                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "15a03eb1499b422f86661",
                    "stepText": "Now, apply the same formula to calculate the wavelength in the muscle layer. Use the provided speed for the muscle layer. What is the wavelength in muscle?",
                    "stepText2": "",
