                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "83465066a1014e33bb4f4",
                    "stepText": "Finally, determine the change in wavelength as the ultrasound wave transitions from fat to muscle by subtracting the wavelength in fat from the wavelength in muscle. What is the resulting change in wavelength?",
